title: TMPGEnc XPress v4.4.2.238 Incl. Keygen and Patch-HAZE
description:
TMPGEnc XPress v4.4.2.238 Incl. Keygen and Patch-HAZE
---------------
           TMPGEnc  4.0  XPress  gives  you the freedom to take almost
           any  video  file  and encode it to your desired file format
           including   DivX  6  AVI,  QuickTime,  MPEG  4-ISO,  H.264,
           DVD-Video,  DVD-VR,  HDV  camcorder,  and  much  more. This
           powerful  software provides you with functions and features
           ranging  from a simple cut-editor tool to multiple powerful
           video filtering and effects.                               
                                             
--------------
Install notes:                                             
           You  should  run  the  app  at least once before generating
           license,  changing license location is a bad idea, licenses
           work  only  on pcs that they were generated on. If you have
           tried  to  use  our older keygen on this version, it&#039;s very
           possible  that  even  after  generating  license  with this
           updated  keygen  something  is  not right (missing formats,
           strange  errors,  bad  output,  etc.).  To  fix this delete
           TMPGEnc4XP_SystemConfig.en.dat    located    in   the  same
           directory with the keyfile.                                
                                                                      
           Install, apply patch and generate a key with the keygen.   
           ...enjoy?
